{"tid":1227550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"還活著的人","createTime":"2019-06-15T15:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:16:31.000Z","uid":260557,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd8f76b04840df6f4523e3e04c1a3c4b6eddfb2","tid":1227550,"uid":260557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"我知好多人為左巴打都好傷心 仲有人話要落去陪佢<br />\n<br />\n但係我想講 要佢唔好枉死<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就更加要好好活著 用每一口氣對抗暴政</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為只有仲有氣先可以出一分力 唔一定好似鄺神咁勁 每個人係可行既崗位盡力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地一定唔可以放棄</span></span>"},{"pid":"c12c87e370c5228fa182da3354d69829840ff9a3","tid":1227550,"uid":14010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"R.I.P"}]}